{"tid":1269924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求文宣組  將今日撐警既生蕃惡行公諸於世","createTime":"2019-06-30T16:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T17:43:23.000Z","uid":53837,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"40b0bc3dba8e0fb14413c79e1192b27a578ba990","tid":1269924,"uid":53837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:59:14.000Z","msg":"求文宣組 將今日班生蕃 比外國人知 <br />\n政府 黑警 黑社會 同 班民建聯加何君妖係一家親<br />\n迫害香港 同污蔑記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日真係睇到好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b6add3cfde59883076b4a80b3988f9ece7e710","tid":1269924,"uid":271912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:59:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">發夢有無人機進入金紫荊上空<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1269833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1269833</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"463c51f8bd7c1c960d8d2330be0457d0d522a665","tid":1269924,"uid":53837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:02:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9b5447a4c5f8cc3b3be3c39a623e43531b0678","tid":1269924,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:02:17.000Z","msg":"[麻煩大家幫手share出去 7月2號就截止申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱</span></strong><br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=0cbba246\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=c07a62cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=1cf42809\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=cf62e221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=6a31f6b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=32fe6eb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / <a href=\"http://FAX.PLUS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FFAX.PLUS&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=9d832722\" target=\"_blank\">http://FAX.PLUS</a> 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=bf26cf91\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<br />\n2016立法會選舉總投票人數都係二百萬人，反送中遊行嘅人如果全部出黎投票嘅話，足以完全改寫立法會！"},{"pid":"ffbff914b74d53169ae5faf3d83f37eab9f6b693","tid":1269924,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"【輿論戰】請廣傳藍絲暴行。連日來和理非，就是為了避免民意流失。現在對家終於犯錯，請快手落井下石。<br />\n<br />\n襲擊林卓廷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1268471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1268471</a><br />\n<br />\n圍毆市民<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UcAbd-S5vVw&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUcAbd-S5vVw%C2%A0&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXM3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=fae389bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UcAbd-S5vVw&nbsp;</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果：多名長者集會後圍毆路過青年 拳打腳踢扯頭髮<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2XbTeJ9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XbTeJ9&